TOOLS:
EMP: Remove all alarm, cant trigger until players next turn ✔
makeup kit: give 1 HP back on current tile  ✔
Crowbar: disable adjustent tile ✔
smoke bomb: 3 stealth token to current tile ✔
virus: 3 token to any computer ✔
blueprint: reveal any tile    ✔
crystal ball: check next 3 event, may shuffle ✔
invisible suit: ignore guard sight for 1 turn(camera), +1 action ✔
therlmal bomb: make stairs up or down, trigger alarm ✔
dynamite: remove wall, trigger alarm ✔
stetoscope: crack a number for safe ✔
rollerskate: +2 action ✔
donut: disable guard for 1 turn ✔


LOOT:
BUST: cant use tools while carrying ✔
stamp: draw event if AP <= 1 ✔
keycard: holder needed for safe rolls ✔
persian cat: roll die end of turn if 1 or 2 move 1 towards alarm ✔
gold bar: place one more, only one can carried by person ✔
cursed goblet: lose 1 HP ✔
mirror: -1 action, not trigger laser ✔
painting: cant use secret door or service duct ✔
isotope: thermo instant alarm ✔
gemstone: 2 action to enter if other player present ✔
tiara: guards see from adjustent tile ✔
chihuahua: end of turn roll die, if 6 trigger alarm ✔

Events:
espresso: guard +1 move this turn ✔
reboot: all computer reset to 1 token ✔
dead drop: give all loot to next player ✔
brown out: remove all alarm, discard guard moves alarm count ✔
shoplifting: trigger alarm on laboratory, if tool taken ✔
time lock: cant use stairs next turn ✔
change of plans: if no alarm, draw next guard move ✔
heads up: next player gets +1 action ✔
video loop: ignore all camera this turn ✔
throw voice: if no alarm, move guard target to adjustent tile ✔
peekhole: peek to any adjustent tile, up or down too ✔
go with your gut: if unrevealed tile adjust, reveal it and move there ✔
keycode change: all keypad reset ✔
crash: trigger alarm on current tile ✔
lampshade: gain HP ✔
buddy system: move a player next to you ✔
squeak: move the guard 1 tile towards closest player ✔
gymnastics: walkway can used as stairs ✔
shift change: guards on other floor move only ✔
switch signs: guard pose and target switch ✔
lost grip: fall a floor ✔
daydreaming: guard -1 move ✔
jump the gun: skip next player's turn ✔
jury-rig: draw a tool ✔
freight elevator: move up 1 floor ✔
where is he?: guard jump to current destination ✔





